    "discogs_id": 59,
    "name": "Kerri Chandler",
    "profile": "DJ and producer from East Orange, New Jersey.\r\nFounded [l=Madhouse Records] in 1992, [l=Sfere] in 1998 (with [l=Dennis Ferrer]). [l=Madtech Records] in 2012 and [l=Kaoz Theory] in 2015.\r\nHis father [a=Joseph Chandler] and uncle [a=Arnold Chandler] were DJs in New York and contributed to [m=170483] in 2002.\r\nHis grandfather [a=Calvin Reed Sr.] aka [a=Grampa] recorded [m=170482] with Kerri in 1993.\r\nKerri's 'Kaoz 6:23' nickname is based on the chaotic events that happened in his life on June 23 every year, early in his career.\r\nFather of [a=Kiki Willows].",
